### Create Invoice
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "invoiceType": "ESTIMATE",
  "status": "PENDING_APPROVAL",
  "totalAmount": 150.00,
  "details": "Oil change and tire rotation",
  "issuedByStaffId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001"
}

### Get All Invoices
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices/

### Get Invoices by Status
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices/?status=PENDING_APPROVAL

### Get Invoice by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Get Invoices by Appointment
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices/appointment/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Update Invoice
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "totalAmount": 160.00,
  "details": "Updated service details",
  "approvedAt": "2023-10-01T10:00:00Z"
}

### Delete Invoice
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000